---
title: Honey-Glazed Turkey Meatballs with Dried Cranberries and Creamy Smashed Potatoes
description: Tender turkey meatballs with a sweet and zesty glaze, creamy smashed potatoes and festive cranberries will remind you of a holiday feast any night of the week!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-glacees-au-miel-34a52b1a.jpg
